---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import BrandMark from "../components/BrandMark.astro";
import InstallBox from "../components/InstallBox.astro";
import { product } from "../data/product";
---
<BaseLayout title="产品预览 — Pipee" description="在浏览器里继续真实的 Pi Session。"><div class="page"><section class="content-hero pad"><span class="eyebrow">Product preview</span><div><h1>你的 Pi，拥有一个浏览器界面。</h1><p>Pipee 呈现真实的 Pi Session、项目和运行过程。它不托管另一套 Agent，也不复制一份 Session 状态。</p></div></section><section class="preview pad content-section"><div class="workspace" aria-label="Pipee 工作台预览"><aside><div class="mini-brand"><BrandMark compact/><strong>pipee</strong></div><nav><span class="active">Sessions</span><span>Projects</span><span>Extensions</span><span>Settings</span></nav><div class="project"><small>CURRENT PROJECT</small><strong>pipee</strong><span>main · clean</span></div></aside><div class="sessions"><header>SESSIONS <b>＋</b></header><article class="active"><i></i><div><strong>重构 Pipee 内页</strong><span>刚刚 · pipee</span></div></article><article><i></i><div><strong>验证发布候选包</strong><span>昨天 · release</span></div></article></div><div class="conversation"><header><div><strong>重构 Pipee 内页</strong><span>Pi Session · /pipee</span></div><b>•••</b></header><div class="messages"><div class="user">让所有页面使用首页建立的设计语言。</div><div class="agent"><span>π</span><div><small>PI</small><p>我会先统一页面结构和信息密度，再逐页移除独立的营销视觉。</p><div class="tool"><b>✓</b><div><strong>Read</strong><small>src/pages</small></div><code>18ms</code></div></div></div></div><div class="composer">告诉 Pi 接下来要做什么… <kbd>⌘ ↵</kbd></div></div><div class="inspector"><header>SESSION</header><div class="ready"><i></i><div><small>STATUS</small><strong>Ready</strong></div></div><dl><div><dt>Model</dt><dd>Claude Sonnet</dd></div><div><dt>Branch</dt><dd>main</dd></div><div><dt>Runtime</dt><dd>Pi</dd></div></dl></div></div></section><section class="features pad content-section"><div class="content-section-head"><span class="eyebrow">What it gives you</span><div><h2>同一个 Session，<br/>多一个工作界面。</h2></div></div><div class="feature-list"><article><span>01</span><h3>继续 Session</h3><p>打开已有对话和项目上下文，不迁移、不重新开始。</p></article><article><span>02</span><h3>观察运行</h3><p>消息、工具调用和状态变化集中呈现。</p></article><article><span>03</span><h3>随时接管</h3><p>Agent 工作时保持可见，需要判断时直接介入。</p></article></div></section><section class="app-install pad content-section"><div><span class="eyebrow">Install</span><h2>安装后运行 <code>{product.cli}</code>。</h2><p>Pipee 在本机运行，连接当前的 Pi 工作环境。</p></div><InstallBox/></section></div></BaseLayout>
<style>.preview{padding-bottom:72px}.workspace{background:#fafaf8;border:1px solid #bdbdb8;border-radius:11px;box-shadow:0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,.06);display:grid;font-size:10px;grid-template-columns:142px 205px 1fr 170px;height:610px;overflow:hidden}.workspace aside{background:#1d1d1c;color:#fff;display:flex;flex-direction:column;padding:18px 12px}.mini-brand{align-items:center;display:flex;font-size:14px;gap:7px;margin:2px 6px 28px}.workspace nav{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:5px}.workspace nav span{border-radius:5px;color:#85857f;padding:9px}.workspace nav .active{background:#333331;color:#fff}.project{border-top:1px solid #3a3a38;display:flex;flex-direction:column;margin-top:auto;padding:16px 6px}.project small,.workspace header{font:700 7px var(--mono);letter-spacing:.08em}.project strong{margin:8px 0 4px}.project span{color:#777771;font-size:8px}.workspace header{align-items:center;border-bottom:1px solid #d7d7d2;display:flex;height:48px;justify-content:space-between;padding:0 15px}.sessions{border-right:1px solid #d7d7d2}.sessions article{align-items:start;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e2dd;display:grid;gap:9px;grid-template-columns:auto 1fr;padding:15px}.sessions article.active{background:#fff}.sessions i{background:#aaa;border-radius:50%;height:6px;margin-top:3px;width:6px}.sessions strong,.sessions span{display:block}.sessions span{color:#8b8b85;font-size:7px;margin-top:5px}.conversation{display:flex;flex-direction:column;min-width:0}.conversation header strong,.conversation header span{display:block}.conversation header span{color:#92928c;font-size:7px;margin-top:4px}.messages{flex:1;padding:34px}.user{background:#e8e8e4;border-radius:8px;line-height:1.6;margin-left:auto;max-width:82%;padding:12px}.agent{display:grid;gap:10px;grid-template-columns:24px 1fr;margin-top:30px}.agent>span{align-items:center;background:var(--ink);border-radius:50%;color:#fff;display:flex;font:14px var(--serif);height:24px;justify-content:center}.agent p{font-size:10px;line-height:1.8}.tool{align-items:center;border:1px solid #d7d7d2;border-radius:6px;display:grid;gap:9px;grid-template-columns:auto 1fr auto;padding:10px}.tool strong,.tool small{display:block}.composer{border:1px solid #c8c8c2;border-radius:7px;color:#969690;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;margin:0 24px 20px;padding:13px}.inspector{border-left:1px solid #d7d7d2}.ready{display:flex;gap:9px;padding:22px 15px}.ready i{background:#4b9a5c;border-radius:50%;height:7px;width:7px}.inspector dl{border-top:1px solid #e2e2dd;margin:0;padding:12px 15px}.inspector dl div{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:7px 0}.inspector dd{margin:0}.features{background:#eeeeeb}.feature-list{border-top:1px solid var(--ink);display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr)}.feature-list article{border-bottom:1px solid var(--ink);border-right:1px solid var(--ink);padding:27px}.feature-list h3{font-size:21px;margin:42px 0 12px}.feature-list p{color:var(--muted);font-size:12px;line-height:1.7}.app-install{align-items:center;display:grid;gap:80px;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}.app-install h2{font-size:clamp(38px,4.5vw,58px);letter-spacing:-.06em;margin:30px 0 18px}.app-install :global(.install-box){max-width:none}@media(max-width:950px){.workspace{grid-template-columns:120px 180px 1fr}.inspector{display:none}}@media(max-width:650px){.workspace{grid-template-columns:72px 1fr;height:520px}.workspace aside nav span{font-size:0}.mini-brand strong,.project,.sessions{display:none}.conversation{grid-column:2}.messages{padding:24px 16px}.feature-list,.app-install{grid-template-columns:1fr}.feature-list article{border-right:0}.app-install{gap:40px}}</style>
